WEBVTT

00:01.500 --> 00:02.030
《越狱》  前情回顾
Previously on Prison Break.

00:02.800 --> 00:03.800
你要"锡拉"做什么
What do you want with Scylla?

00:03.860 --> 00:06.030
和你一样  打垮"公司"
Same thing you want: bring down the Company.

00:06.100 --> 00:07.260
我们需要那几页
We need the pages.

00:07.330 --> 00:08.430
我们一起合作吗
Are we partners?

00:09.330 --> 00:10.530
是的
Partners.

00:10.600 --> 00:12.400
你哥哥跟我说了你流鼻血的事
So your brother told me about your nosebleeds.

00:12.460 --> 00:13.860
我很好
I'm fine.

00:13.930 --> 00:15.100
你看起来可不好
You don't look fine.

00:16.360 --> 00:17.030
对不起
Sorry.

00:17.100 --> 00:18.130
引以为戒吧
Consider this a warning.

00:21.330 --> 00:22.300
林肯  倒回去
Linc, pull back!

00:22.360 --> 00:23.300
是个圈套
It's a trap!

00:23.360 --> 00:24.630
快走  林肯
Come on, Linc!

00:24.700 --> 00:25.600
等一下
Hang on!

00:25.660 --> 00:27.960
你没事吧  你中枪了
You all right?! Damn, you're hit!

00:31.430 --> 00:33.400
好了  好了
All right, all right.

00:33.460 --> 00:35.330
你会有机会收拾他的  退后
You'll get your shot, now back off!

00:35.400 --> 00:38.060
他们是想拿我的卡
This is an attempt on my card.

00:38.130 --> 00:39.200
接下来你想怎么办
How do you want to proceed?

00:39.260 --> 00:40.260
我要转移它
I want it moved.

00:40.330 --> 00:42.030
转移"锡拉"
Move Scylla.

00:42.100 --> 00:43.460
现在
Now!

00:50.930 --> 00:54.060
告诉将军你把我们都干掉了
Now, tell the General you killed us.

00:54.130 --> 00:56.900
否则  我的手可不会歇着
Otherwise, my hand, it ain't going to get tired.

00:56.960 --> 01:00.630
我觉得你的嘴该歇歇了
I just hope your mouth gets tired.

01:02.830 --> 01:04.660
很搞笑
That's funny.

01:07.730 --> 01:09.600
走吧  老兄  走吧
Come on, buddy, come on.

01:09.660 --> 01:10.630
够了  我们走吧  林肯
Enough already, come on, Linc.

01:16.530 --> 01:18.130
现在相信我了吧
Believe me now?

01:18.200 --> 01:20.760
打他是没有用的  林肯
Beating him isn't going to work, Lincoln.

01:20.860 --> 01:22.400
你的方法也用过了
You tried your way.

01:22.460 --> 01:25.030
我们要让克兰兹将军相信怀特已经把我们解决了
We want General Krantz to think Wyatt took us out.

01:25.030 --> 01:28.200
就算你把他打到给将军打电话
Even if you do beat him to make the call to general.

01:28.200 --> 01:29.760
你觉得一个训练有素的军人
you don't think a trained military veteran

01:29.830 --> 01:31.460
听不出他话里的恐惧吗
is going to hear the fear in his voice?

01:31.530 --> 01:33.700
他们会知道他是被强迫的
They're going to know he was coerced.

01:33.700 --> 01:38.000
对付他要多点时间
Yeah,well.I need some more time with him.

01:38.000 --> 01:40.860
我明白  林肯  但是他神志不清的话也不能打电话
I hear you, Linc, but he can't make the call if he's unconscious.

01:40.930 --> 01:42.660
不管我们怎么做
However we do it,

01:42.730 --> 01:44.800
我们最好快点从怀特那里得到我们想要的
we better get what we need from Wyatt soon,

01:44.860 --> 01:46.700
马宏可等不及了
because Mahone ain't going to wait.

01:51.360 --> 01:54.060
我要找到那个杀我儿子的贱人
I'm trying to find the son of a bitch who killed my kid!

01:57.860 --> 01:59.830
丽莎  情况如何
Lisa, what are we looking at?

01:59.900 --> 02:02.030
初步估计转移"锡拉"大概要三天
Initial estimate is three days to complete the move of Scylla.

02:02.100 --> 02:03.900
我不能接受
Unacceptable.

02:05.330 --> 02:08.700
请听我说  这可不像把一台电脑
Respectfully, this is not as simple as unplugging

02:08.760 --> 02:11.000
从一间房挪到另一间房那么简单
a laptop and moving it to another room.

02:11.060 --> 02:12.400
"锡拉"里的数据太复杂了
The data on Scylla is too delicate.

02:12.460 --> 02:14.200
我不想听理由
I don't want excuses.

02:14.260 --> 02:17.400
我只关心  它能否妥善转移以及是否现在就转移
All I care is that it's done right and done right now.

02:17.460 --> 02:20.200
我明白这很紧急  但也要三天时间
I understand the urgency, but it will take three days.

02:20.260 --> 02:22.360
请允许我说几句  我觉得
And if I may speak freely, I think it's a mistake

02:22.430 --> 02:24.360
把"锡拉"转移到拉文罗克地堡
to move Scylla to the Raven Rock bunker

02:24.430 --> 02:25.800
而放弃对我们来说最安全的洛城
when the Los Angeles facility

02:25.860 --> 02:27.400
是一个错误
is one of the most secure ones we have.

02:27.460 --> 02:29.400
对我们来说最安全的地方
The most secure location we have

02:29.460 --> 02:31.060
就是不为人知的地方
is the one they don't know about.

02:31.130 --> 02:32.930
长官
Sir...

02:33.000 --> 02:34.000
还是没有怀特的消息
Still no word from Wyatt.

02:34.060 --> 02:35.230
他只用"公司"提供的电话
He only uses the company-issued cell,

02:35.300 --> 02:36.530
我们追踪不到他
so we can't track him.

02:36.600 --> 02:38.200
我们无法确定
We have no way of confirming

02:38.260 --> 02:39.900
他是否完成了任务
if he successfully completed his operation.

02:39.960 --> 02:40.800
继续联系
Keep calling him!

02:40.860 --> 02:42.000
准备一份新闻稿
And draft a press release,

02:42.060 --> 02:43.500
照片  犯罪记录
photographs, criminal records,

02:43.560 --> 02:45.860
所有关于斯科菲尔德  布伦斯等人的全部资料
everything we have on Scofield, Burrows, all of them.

02:45.930 --> 02:47.660
告诉媒体的朋友  我要他们
Tell our friends in the media I want them

02:47.730 --> 02:50.200
在晚间新闻和早报里都报导
to saturate the evening news and the morning papers.

02:50.260 --> 02:51.900
我要让他们不能
I want it impossible for them

02:51.960 --> 02:54.760
大摇大摆的走在洛城的街道上
to walk down the streets of Los Angeles without being spotted.

03:01.200 --> 03:03.600
我猜我们还没在他身上
I assume we haven't made much progress

03:03.660 --> 03:05.260
得到任何进展
with our friend over there?

03:05.330 --> 03:06.130
有什么建议吗
Any suggestions?

03:06.200 --> 03:08.260
要不我们和他谈谈
How about we talk to him?

03:08.330 --> 03:10.430
好啊  要不要给他点牛奶和饼干
Great, want to give him some milk and cookies while you're at it?

03:10.500 --> 03:11.760
不是
No.

03:11.830 --> 03:14.460
随便聊聊怎么样
How about just some nice conversation?

