03:45.200 --> 03:48.160
《越狱》第四季 第九集
Prison.Break.S04E09

04:00.300 --> 04:02.600
他们就叫个护士
So they sent Florence Nightingale

04:02.660 --> 04:06.100
来让我乖乖合作
to get me all ready to cooperate.

04:06.160 --> 04:08.800
实际上   不管你做了什么  我是来帮你的
Actually, I'm here to help you, despite what you've done.

04:08.860 --> 04:10.700
因为我还是医生  而你是囚犯
Because I'm still a doctor and you're a prisoner.

04:10.760 --> 04:12.460
你想要救我
You're going to save me?

04:12.530 --> 04:14.260
唐·赛尔夫带了个箱子来
Don Self has a metal case out there

04:14.330 --> 04:15.760
我不知道里面有什么
and I don't know what's in it.

04:15.830 --> 04:17.300
我猜你也不会想知道
I imagine you don't want to find out,

04:17.360 --> 04:19.630
所以  我想我们要是谈谈
so I figure if you and I had a talk...

04:19.700 --> 04:21.160
你会给我一线生机
You'd make me see the light.

04:21.230 --> 04:24.530
你要是不给将军打电话  你就死定了
If you don't call the General, you're as good as dead.

04:24.600 --> 04:30.590
我早经历过很多生不如死的事  医生
I've already been a lot of things worse than dead in my life, Doctor.

04:32.030 --> 04:34.660
你还是找个好点的理由来威胁我
You better have more than that to threaten me with.

04:38.260 --> 04:39.430
放心  迈克尔  她没事的
Come on, Mike, she's okay.

04:39.500 --> 04:41.060
他是个职业杀手
He's a professional killer.

04:41.130 --> 04:42.460
不用担心  他已经被拷起来了
Don't worry, he's locked up.

04:42.530 --> 04:43.700
我们走吧
Let's go.

04:45.230 --> 04:47.200
快点  我们走吧
Come on, let's go!

04:47.260 --> 04:49.600
你想怎么处理罗兰的尸体
So what'd you do with Roland's body?

04:49.660 --> 04:50.800
罗兰
Roland?

04:50.860 --> 04:54.060
他的资料已经全改了
He's been, uh, reconfigured

04:54.130 --> 04:55.900
而且埋在一个长眠之地
and given a permanent resting place.

04:55.960 --> 04:57.160
太好了  你走的时候顺便
Good. Take his bowling shirts

04:57.230 --> 04:58.830
把他的衣物和他的垃圾也带走
and the rest of his crap with you when you leave.

04:58.900 --> 05:01.200
算了吧  林肯  人都死了
Come on Linc, the guy died.

05:01.260 --> 05:03.560
他出卖了我们  死有余辜  贝里克
He died a punk! He ratted us out, Bellick.

05:03.630 --> 05:05.530
各位  我们先处理眼前的事
You guys, you deal with the matter at hand.

05:07.530 --> 05:09.460
假设这几张纸是正确的
Assuming these pages are correct,

05:09.530 --> 05:11.400
我们也无从考证它们是不是真的
and there's no way of knowing that they actually are...

05:13.060 --> 05:15.230
我们从地下走廊  通过锅炉房到这
we follow this basement hallway through the boiler room to here.

05:15.300 --> 05:17.200
这里是往上走的爬梯
There's some kind of elevated walkway.

05:17.260 --> 05:18.500
我们顺着走到底
We follow that to the end,

05:18.560 --> 05:20.600
这样我们就涵盖了大部分
and we've covered most of the distance

05:20.660 --> 05:22.360
从伽特到"公司"总部间的距离
between GATE and the Company's headquarters.

05:22.430 --> 05:24.430
走廊尽头的是什么东西
What's this thing at the end of the walkway?

05:24.500 --> 05:26.500
我也不知道  惠斯勒用X做了个标记
I don't know-- Whistler marked it with an "X"

05:26.560 --> 05:29.500
我想可能是面墙或大的障碍物
so I'm thinking it's some kind of wall or serious impediment.

05:29.560 --> 05:31.330
所以我们要下去做好准备
That's why we're going down there prepared.

05:31.400 --> 05:34.160
工具  电焊  锤子
Tools, thermal lances, sledgehammers...

05:34.230 --> 05:35.600
就算我们穿过了墙
Okay, so we get through that wall...

05:35.660 --> 05:36.760
另一边是什么
what's on the other side?

05:36.830 --> 05:38.600
我还不知道
Again, I don't know.

05:38.660 --> 05:40.600
因为剩下的几页在格雷琴手里
It's because Gretchen has the rest of the pages.

05:40.660 --> 05:42.260
但是一旦我们通过这个地方
But once we're through this location,

05:42.330 --> 05:44.260
除非她把几页纸给我们  否则就无法前进
we can't go any further until she gives them back.

05:44.330 --> 05:45.500
她到底耍什么诡计
What's her game in all this?

05:45.560 --> 05:47.600
如果她想把"公司"搞垮
I mean, if she wants the Company to go down,

05:47.660 --> 05:49.130
她就应该把几页纸给我们
she should just give us the pages.

05:49.200 --> 05:50.500
只要时机成熟
Look, we're going to deal with Gretchen

05:50.560 --> 05:51.930
我们就解决格雷琴
when the time is right, okay?

05:52.000 --> 05:53.530
你们要
You guys need

05:53.600 --> 05:54.660
去伽特开始准备
to go to GATE and get started.

05:54.730 --> 05:55.700
我留下来看着怀特
I'm going to stay here with Wyatt

05:55.760 --> 05:56.800
确保从他嘴里套有用的东西
and make sure we get what we need.

06:02.200 --> 06:03.500
从现在开始不能乱串
No more dawdlin' now.

06:03.560 --> 06:04.900
走快点
Move your ass.

06:04.960 --> 06:07.160
快点  先生们  快点
High gear, gentlemen, high gear.

06:07.230 --> 06:08.800
我老板随时可能会来
My boss will be here any minute.

06:12.400 --> 06:17.830
我想我不用重申谨慎行事至关重要
I assume I don't have to mention that discretion is paramount.

06:17.900 --> 06:21.560
换句话说  "沉默"是金
In other words, silence is golden.

06:21.630 --> 06:24.260
你只要确保在办公室里呆着
You just make sure you stay in your office

06:24.330 --> 06:25.900
别让别人进来
and you keep other people out.

06:25.960 --> 06:27.300
我会呆在舒适
Oh, I'll stay in my nice,

06:27.360 --> 06:28.800
凉快的办公室里的  小白脸
air-conditioned office, Pretty.

06:28.860 --> 06:30.700
你现在可以爬你的小洞里去了
And you can crawl down into your little hole now.

06:31.500 --> 06:32.600
快
Go ahead.

06:32.660 --> 06:35.430
快
Go ahead.

06:35.500 --> 06:37.360
快  爬吧
Go ahead, crawl.

06:44.000 --> 06:47.560
科尔  这里到底出什么事了
Cole? What the hell is going on here?

06:47.630 --> 06:49.660
怀特先生  你回来了
Mr. White, are you back already?

06:49.730 --> 06:50.830
你好吗
How are you?

06:50.900 --> 06:52.500
很好  直到我收到一封安德鲁·布劳努
Fine, until I found a resignation fax

06:52.560 --> 06:56.030
发来的辞职传真
waiting for me from Andrew Blauner.

06:57.030 --> 06:58.000
辞职信
A resignation?

06:58.060 --> 06:59.530
对  打电话也不接
Yeah, I can't get him on the phone,

06:59.600 --> 07:01.000
我打给他未婚妻
I reached out to his fiancee,

07:01.060 --> 07:02.400
她也不知道没有他的消息
she hasn't seen or heard from him.

07:02.460 --> 07:04.200
她非常担心
She's worried sick.

07:04.260 --> 07:06.400
他可能就是喝大了
He's probably on a bit of a bender,

07:06.460 --> 07:07.660
睡在什么地方了
just sleeping it off somewhere.

07:07.730 --> 07:09.530
布劳努可是名童子军
Blauner? He's a Boy Scout.

07:09.600 --> 07:11.430
这不合逻辑  科尔
None of this makes any sense, Cole.

07:11.500 --> 07:13.500
不过我告诉你
But I'll tell you what,

07:13.560 --> 07:15.330
我会查清楚的
I'm going to look into it.

07:18.700 --> 07:20.260
有需要我帮忙的地方  就告诉我
Let me know if I can be of any assistance.

07:20.330 --> 07:21.930
早上好
Good morning.

07:22.000 --> 07:23.660
帮忙
Assistance...

07:31.960 --> 07:34.060
那是什么声音
What is that sound?

07:46.130 --> 07:47.230
喂
Yeah?

07:47.300 --> 07:50.230
我希望能有个愉快的早晨
I hope you're having a lovely enjoyable morning,

07:50.300 --> 07:51.560
因为你不在的时候
because while you are nowhere to be found,

07:51.630 --> 07:52.930
这边已经在调查
there is sleuthing going on here

07:53.000 --> 07:55.100
安德鲁·布劳努的下落了
regarding the whereabouts of one Mr. Andrew Blauner.

07:55.160 --> 07:56.960
还有吗
And?

07:57.030 --> 07:58.660
如果我卷进这起凶杀案的话
And if I'm going down for this little homicide,

07:58.730 --> 08:00.000
我可不会一个人背黑锅
I ain't going alone.

08:00.060 --> 08:01.660
我们肯定是形影不离的
We're going together like traffic and weather.

08:01.730 --> 08:02.930
放松点  好吗
Relax, okay?

08:03.000 --> 08:05.460
他们绝对找不到我放尸体的地方
They'll never find the body where I put it.

08:05.530 --> 08:08.830
斯科菲尔德和布伦斯现在在哪
Now, where are Scofield and Burrows?

08:08.900 --> 08:10.660
正在履行他们的承诺
Just doing their end of the bargain.

08:10.730 --> 08:13.200
顺便问一下  你到底在干嘛
Which begs the question, what the hell are you doing?

08:13.260 --> 08:15.260
我
Me?

08:19.000 --> 08:20.960
我准备去会一个人
I'm getting ready for a meeting.

08:23.900 --> 08:27.100
你朋友一直打电话给你
So, your friends have been calling a lot.

08:27.160 --> 08:29.200
他们一定在想你到哪儿去了
They must be wondering where you are.

08:29.260 --> 08:30.430
没错
That's right.

08:30.500 --> 08:33.330
他们在怀疑  而他们怀疑得越久
They're wondering, and the longer they do,

08:33.400 --> 08:34.930
你们就越危险
the more danger you're in.

08:35.000 --> 08:37.530
打电话给将军  照他们的话说
Call the General, and say what they want you to say.

08:37.600 --> 08:39.600
然后呢  你们会放我走吗
And what? You'll let me go?

08:39.660 --> 08:41.760
不会  但唐·赛尔夫能确保
No, but Don Self will make sure

08:41.830 --> 08:43.000
你免于死刑
that you spend the rest of your life

08:43.060 --> 08:45.200
下半辈子悠闲自在
in a decent facility without the death penalty.

08:47.130 --> 08:48.630
无论如何
Either way,

08:48.700 --> 08:50.960
无论我打不打这通电话
if I make the call or not,

08:51.030 --> 08:53.030
我都会死
I'm dead.

08:53.100 --> 08:54.700
你心里明白的很
You know that.

08:54.760 --> 08:58.700
我们都清楚  你作为一名医生
And we both know that you, as a doctor,

08:58.760 --> 09:00.730
不会容许这种事情发生
won't let that happen.

09:00.800 --> 09:02.760
所以  不如
So, please,

09:02.830 --> 09:04.830
我们一起想个
let's you and I figure a way

09:04.900 --> 09:10.000
互惠互利的解决办法
out of this mess that works for everybody.

09:34.060 --> 09:35.660
-坐好  -别挡路
Sit your ass down! Get out of my way!

09:35.730 --> 09:36.960
别 别这样
Out! Out!

09:37.030 --> 09:39.300
不然我会把你按在桌子上的
I will cuff your ass to that table, okay?

09:39.360 --> 09:40.960
我知道这很痛苦
All right, I know this is hard.

09:41.030 --> 09:42.930
我也知道你想干什么
And I know what you want to do.

09:43.000 --> 09:44.800
可是我们正在努力做事
Okay, but I'm trying to do something here

09:44.860 --> 09:46.530
你必须接受现实
and you need to deal with that reality.

09:46.600 --> 09:48.260
你有失去孩子吗
Have you lost a kid?

09:48.330 --> 09:49.330
我失去过
Yeah, I did, too.

09:49.400 --> 09:52.700
我老婆当时怀孕
My wife was pregnant.

09:52.760 --> 09:55.830
她有并发症  而那个庸医不会处理
And there were complications and the doctor messed up.

