23:13.650 --> 23:15.190
应该就在主管道附近
should be somewhere near the main conduit.

23:15.250 --> 23:17.220
你觉得这个像主管道吗
This look like the main conduit to you?

23:17.290 --> 23:19.520
有办法弄明白
One way to find out.

23:30.650 --> 23:32.650
你觉得这个像吗
That look like it to you?

23:32.720 --> 23:33.690
像
Looks like it.

23:33.750 --> 23:34.950
把它点着
Fire it up.

23:46.920 --> 23:48.790
好了  我们走吧
All right, let's get out of here.

23:49.850 --> 23:51.120
快点  哥们
Hurry up, bro!

23:51.190 --> 23:53.120
就快好了 兄弟
Almost done, buddy.

23:53.190 --> 23:54.950
好了  把它挪回去
All right, ease it back.

24:09.520 --> 24:11.020
搞定了
It worked.

24:12.920 --> 24:14.950
我们有多长时间
How long we got?

24:16.020 --> 24:19.350
不清楚
I don't know.

24:19.420 --> 24:21.650
千万人的水源被切断
Water cut off to thousands of people.

24:21.720 --> 24:24.190
政府会在一个小时左右抢修
The city will probably have that taken care of in about an hour,

24:24.250 --> 24:27.650
意味着我们有60分钟
which means we've got... 60 minutes

24:27.720 --> 24:29.590
做90分钟的工作
to do 90 minutes worth of work.

24:29.650 --> 24:31.820
否则我们就得不到"锡拉"
Or we don't get to Scylla.

24:43.050 --> 24:44.650
怎么了  老兄
What's wrong, papi?

24:51.890 --> 24:54.690
迈克
Mike.

24:54.750 --> 24:56.990
迈克尔  迈克尔
Michael! Michael!

24:57.050 --> 24:58.550
怎么了  兄弟
What's wrong, papi?!

24:58.620 --> 24:59.890
兄弟  说话啊
Papi, talk to me!

24:59.950 --> 25:01.920
你怎么了  说话啊
What's wrong?! Talk to me!

25:01.990 --> 25:02.950
迈克尔
Michael!

25:03.020 --> 25:06.520
迈克尔  你怎么了
Michael, what's wrong?!

25:15.720 --> 25:18.160
想喝水吗
You want some water?

25:18.220 --> 25:19.820
我没事
I'm okay.

25:19.890 --> 25:22.020
兄弟  你现在背负过重
You're a lot of things right now, my friend,

25:22.090 --> 25:24.390
而却没有背负"没事"
and okay ain't one of them.

25:24.460 --> 25:30.860
你知道  我可能不是最聪明的人
You know, I may not be the smartest guy,

25:30.920 --> 25:32.790
但我听到了
but I hear things.

25:32.860 --> 25:35.220
莎拉和你哥哥
Sara and your brother

25:35.290 --> 25:39.620
谈过有关你的身体健康的问题
have been talking about you not feeling well or something.

25:39.690 --> 25:43.690
听着  我只是  只是说说
Look, I'm just, I'm just saying.

25:49.590 --> 25:52.720
我需要你帮忙
I need your help.

25:52.790 --> 25:56.460
所以  请你
So, please, just, uh...

25:56.520 --> 25:58.820
帮我瞒着
...cover for me.

25:58.820 --> 26:00.820
没问题
You got it.

26:12.420 --> 26:16.590
事实上  格雷琴  我比你更了解你自己
Truth is, Gretchen, I know you better than you know yourself.

26:17.620 --> 26:20.320
你一直这么跟我说
So you keep telling me.

26:20.390 --> 26:23.620
我初次见你时  你才20岁
When I first met you, you were a 20 year old girl

26:23.690 --> 26:25.760
由于心理评估失败
who'd just been dumped by the Wheeling Police Academy

26:25.820 --> 26:28.920
你被惠灵警官学院开除了
for failing her psych evaluation.

26:28.990 --> 26:32.490
但那些佛吉尼亚老脑筋
But where those good old West Virginia boys

26:32.560 --> 26:35.890
只能看出一种具有
could only see an emotional disconnect

26:35.960 --> 26:38.590
反社会倾向的情绪反常
with traces of sociopathic tendencies,

26:38.660 --> 26:42.360
我看到的是一个能
I saw a Machiavellian streak

26:42.420 --> 26:44.790
让失败成为不可能的足智多谋的人
that would make failure an impossibility.

26:44.860 --> 26:47.420
我只能让怀特那么做
I had to let Wyatt do what he did

26:47.490 --> 26:48.820
因为我想知道
because I needed to know...

26:50.890 --> 26:53.720
是否我的斗牛犬已得知惠斯勒
...what my little bulldog may have known

26:53.790 --> 26:56.720
以及他想得到关锡拉的计划
about Whistler and his plans for Scylla.

26:57.890 --> 27:01.420
我说过我什么也不知道
I told you that I knew nothing.

27:01.490 --> 27:03.860
你应该相信我
You should have believed me.

27:03.920 --> 27:06.760
我知道你从不义气用事
I knew you'd never take it personally,

27:06.820 --> 27:11.660
因为从你成为我的左右手开始
because you are, and have been

27:11.720 --> 27:16.360
你就是  也一直是
ever since I took you under my wing...

27:16.420 --> 27:18.090
我的女人
...my girl.

27:32.120 --> 27:33.990
我的女人
My girl.

27:42.390 --> 27:44.560
最敏感的神经末梢就在这里
The most sensitive nerve endings are right here.

27:44.620 --> 27:47.320
这就是为什么针灸医生都会避免
That's why acupuncturists avoid placing needles

27:47.390 --> 27:49.120
在任何接近这个位置用针  因为
anywhere near them because opening up

27:49.190 --> 27:51.220
指尖的神经末端
the nerve endings in the fingertip--

27:51.290 --> 27:52.720
就算只刺到一点
even a little pinprick--

27:52.790 --> 27:56.160
都能引起极大的灼热痛楚
can result in quite a painful hot flash.

27:57.790 --> 27:58.960
所以一根5英寸长的针
So a five inch needle

27:59.020 --> 28:01.390
插入一指的长度
being driven up the length of the finger...

28:05.190 --> 28:08.160
能让你体内感觉被火燃烧一般
...can make your insides feel like they're on fire.

28:09.520 --> 28:11.090
生理学的另一方面说
Another fact of physiology,

28:11.160 --> 28:13.860
当人体无法承受极端的压迫时会休克
the human body when in extreme duress begins to shut down.

28:13.920 --> 28:18.190
大脑活动减弱  心率也会下降
Brain activity decreases and your heart rate slows

28:18.260 --> 28:20.460
直到你再也感觉不到疼痛
until you just can't feel the pain anymore.

28:20.520 --> 28:22.490
这就是心电图和电击的作用
And that's where the heart monitor and the battery come in.

28:22.560 --> 28:24.820
因为当你的心率降到50以下
'Cause when your heart rate dips below 50,

28:24.890 --> 28:27.520
电击就会给你一个苏醒的信号
that battery will give you a wake-up call,

28:27.590 --> 28:29.660
避免你的身体休克
preventing your body from shutting down.

28:29.720 --> 28:33.390
你才能感受到任何一丁点的
And then you will feel every ounce...

28:33.460 --> 28:35.390
疼痛
of the pain.

28:37.120 --> 28:39.720
到时候你会求着让我打电话
And that's when you're going to beg me to make the phone call.

28:53.220 --> 28:54.620
有什么可以帮你吗
What can I do you for?

28:56.020 --> 28:57.360
我在你的销售报告里找到
I... I found some more inconsistencies

28:57.420 --> 28:58.490
一些矛盾的地方
in your sales reports.

29:08.620 --> 29:09.760
听着
Listen up here.

29:09.820 --> 29:11.190
你的电脑可不可以
From that little computer of yours,

29:11.260 --> 29:13.120
读取伽特的数据
can you access into GATE's records?

29:14.560 --> 29:16.790
如果用管理员身份登陆的话
If I access the network as an administrator,

29:16.860 --> 29:19.060
我能以非pdf格式浏览文件
I can see the files in a non-PDF format.

29:19.120 --> 29:21.390
我不知道什么意思  但我认为你可以办到
I don't know what that means, but I assume it was a yes.

29:21.460 --> 29:23.890
所以随你怎么敲键盘
So you let your fingers do the walking across that keyboard

29:23.960 --> 29:25.360
把我的销售报告拿给我
and you get me my sales records.

29:25.420 --> 29:26.460
你弄伤我的手臂了
You are hurting my arm.

29:26.520 --> 29:28.320
最好别让我伤害其他部位
And don't make me hurt any more of you.

29:28.390 --> 29:29.560
现在就去
Now, go.

29:50.620 --> 29:52.090
做的好
That's good work.

30:05.920 --> 30:07.920
给
Here.

30:13.360 --> 30:15.160
我要你测量下这个洞
I need you to measure this hole.

30:16.960 --> 30:20.220
在对面的墙上打个同等大小的洞
And then make one of the same size in the wall opposite.

30:20.290 --> 30:21.590
怎么弄
How?

30:21.660 --> 30:24.120
你有系腰带吧
You got a belt?

30:26.220 --> 30:28.790
好了
Okay.

30:50.890 --> 30:52.990
在水再次灌满水管之前
We have less than 30 minutes

30:53.060 --> 30:56.320
我们还有不到半小时时间
until this pipe is flooded with water again.

31:25.790 --> 31:27.860
接受现实是很重要的  怀特
Acceptance is important, Wyatt.

31:27.920 --> 31:31.320
我必须接受我儿子已经死了
I had to accept that my son is gone.

31:31.390 --> 31:33.790
而你也必须接受你的生命
And you have to accept that your life,

31:33.860 --> 31:37.560
你所剩无几的生命
your very, very short life-span ahead of you

31:37.620 --> 31:41.260
将充满无法忍受的疼痛
is just going to be filled with agonizing pain.

31:41.320 --> 31:44.060
直到你按我的要求去做
At least until you do what I've asked of you.

31:44.120 --> 31:47.560
到那时
And then...

31:47.620 --> 31:50.720
痛苦将会离你而去
then the pain will go away.

31:59.620 --> 32:01.090
我们快没时间了
We're running out of time!

32:05.890 --> 32:07.160
-不会吧  -怎么了
- Man.  - What's wrong?

32:08.220 --> 32:09.590
这该死的东西居然空了
The stupid thing is empty!

32:10.660 --> 32:12.680
那么
All right.

32:12.680 --> 32:13.900
我进去吧
I'm coming in.

32:29.120 --> 32:31.060
老兄  你不行了
You can't do this, bro.

32:32.120 --> 32:33.290
赶紧干完再说
Just finish it.

32:41.220 --> 32:43.720
喂
Hello?

32:43.790 --> 32:45.020
是我
It's me.

32:45.090 --> 32:46.820
怎么了
What's going on?

32:46.890 --> 32:50.820
有人要告诉你一些事
Somebody needs to tell you something.

32:53.860 --> 32:55.760
用她的姓称呼她
You call her by her first name.

33:02.290 --> 33:03.460
潘姆
Pam...

33:07.520 --> 33:12.020
我很抱歉
I'm... sorry.

33:17.190 --> 33:19.060
一切都结束了
It's over.

33:20.090 --> 33:22.060
我爱你
And I love you.

33:24.960 --> 33:27.290
我爱你
I love you.

33:49.560 --> 33:51.190
这东西太沉了
This thing is heavy!

33:52.990 --> 33:55.160
太好了  苦力活干完了你们才来
Sure, show up when all the hard work is done.

33:55.220 --> 33:57.220
好了  松后点
All right, ease it back.

33:57.290 --> 33:58.590
我们听电台说
We heard on the radio

33:58.660 --> 34:01.320
水利部门会在10分钟内恢复供水
that DWP is going to have the water running in 10 minutes.

34:04.790 --> 34:05.760
你没事吧
You all right?

34:06.820 --> 34:09.360
管子太重了
The sleeve is too heavy

34:09.420 --> 34:10.990
很难塞过排水管
to just slide it through the pipe.

34:11.060 --> 34:13.760
必须有2个人进去
Two of us are going to have to go inside

34:13.820 --> 34:15.490
引它穿过另一个洞口
and guide it through that other hole.

34:15.560 --> 34:17.090
水流随时可能从排水管冲过来
That pipe can flood at any time.

34:18.160 --> 34:19.360
我上
I'll do it.

34:19.420 --> 34:20.420
我也上
I'll go, too.

34:21.820 --> 34:22.790
不  让我来
No, I'll go.

34:22.860 --> 34:24.590
优等生  并非冒犯
Oh, no offense, college boy,

34:24.660 --> 34:26.260
但这大家伙太重了
but this sucker's heavy.

34:26.320 --> 34:27.760
你得再强壮点才行
You're going to need a little bulk down there.

34:27.820 --> 34:30.020
好吧
All right.

34:32.560 --> 34:34.020
你们把它推过另一边时
Use this to brace the sleeve

34:34.090 --> 34:35.920
用这个支撑水管
when you pull it through to the other side.

34:35.990 --> 34:41.190
然后  我们一起离开这里  好吗
And Let's get the hell out of there, all right?

34:49.190 --> 34:51.160
艾咪还好吗
How's Emmy?

34:51.220 --> 34:53.120
我来这不是听你
I didn't come here to listen to you

34:53.190 --> 34:57.460
假装关心她  或关心我
Pretend to care about her...or me.

34:59.220 --> 35:02.590
我来此是要告诉你  我是现在是空闲探员
I came here to tell you that I'm a free agent now.

35:02.660 --> 35:05.620
我们经营的集团知道我还活着且可以雇用
The community we run with know that I'm alive and available.

35:07.390 --> 35:11.690
我可以像为你卖命一样为他们卖命
I can just as easily work for one of them as I can for you.

35:11.760 --> 35:13.990
所以问题在于  你出价多少
So the question is, what's your offer?

35:14.060 --> 35:17.120
实际上  你的问题是
Actually, the question for you is

35:17.190 --> 35:18.790
何必去其他地方呢
why would you want to go anywhere else?

35:18.860 --> 35:21.290
现在不是记仇的时候  格雷琴
It's not a time for grudges, Gretchen.

35:21.360 --> 35:23.920
是我们联手的时机
It's a time for coming together.

35:23.990 --> 35:26.660
好日子就快到来了
The salad days are fast approaching.

35:26.720 --> 35:28.160
老挝那边进展顺利
Laos worked perfectly.

35:29.390 --> 35:31.520
民众很快会投奔我们
Soon the populace will turn to us--

35:31.590 --> 35:32.920
军队  财政  能源的首领们
the leaders of the military,

35:32.990 --> 35:35.990
都会与我们为伍
finance and energy-- to right the ship.

35:36.060 --> 35:37.790
然后
And then...

35:37.860 --> 35:40.860
我们就能依我们的设想重建这个国家
we'll rebuild this country in our own image.

35:40.920 --> 35:44.190
格雷琴  我希望那时你可以在我身边
And when we do, I want you there beside me, Gretchen.

35:44.260 --> 35:47.220
如我许诺过的  做我的副手
As my number two, like I always promised.

35:47.290 --> 35:49.020
丽莎呢
What about Lisa?

35:49.090 --> 35:52.760
我已经跟你说了
I've already told you.

35:52.820 --> 35:54.890
你才是我的女人
You're my girl.

36:06.220 --> 36:09.220
出来
Come on.

36:12.290 --> 36:14.690
去那边
Over there.

36:21.360 --> 36:23.360
就站那儿
Right up there.

36:34.760 --> 36:36.860
你和我都是同一类人
You and I are the same,

36:36.920 --> 36:38.990
阿历克斯
Alex.

36:39.060 --> 36:40.920
我做过的事
I've done things...

37:01.090 --> 37:02.390
用力推
Push!

37:02.460 --> 37:04.560
继续推  继续
Keep going, keep going!

37:07.190 --> 37:09.420
继续推  继续
Keep going! Keep going!

37:09.490 --> 37:11.020
很好  就这样
Yeah, it's good right there.

37:11.090 --> 37:11.860
够到了吗
You got it?

37:11.920 --> 37:13.190
就这样
That's it.

37:13.260 --> 37:14.960
我不知道这个能撑多久
I don't know how long that's going to hold.

37:20.790 --> 37:22.960
我们只要把这个拉过去就行了
All we got to do is pull this thing through.

37:23.020 --> 37:25.360
大家用力推
Oh, guys, push!

37:28.260 --> 37:29.490
断了
Oh! It broke!

37:29.490 --> 37:31.080
木桩断了
The brace is broke!

37:42.560 --> 37:45.620
怀特先生
Mr. White...

37:45.690 --> 37:48.390
很抱歉打扰你  我和莫拉侦探谈过后
I'm sorry to bother you, but, uh, after my talk

37:48.460 --> 37:50.890
我一直在想布劳努先生
with Detective Mara, I was thinking about Mr. Blauner

37:50.960 --> 37:53.520
和我之间的谈话
and some of the conversations we had.

37:53.590 --> 37:55.560
推销员和渔夫很相似  不是吗
Salesmen are a lot like fishermen, right?

37:55.620 --> 37:57.260
总是对自己的业绩夸夸其谈
Always bragging about their big catch.

37:58.420 --> 38:01.860
但安迪却闭口不提他的业绩
Well, Andy never talked about his sales,

38:01.920 --> 38:03.890
无论我如何旁敲侧击
No matter how much I pried.

38:03.960 --> 38:07.490
所以我擅自查了一下
So I took the liberty of... looking them up.

38:10.060 --> 38:13.290
表面  至少存在一些
And there were, to say the least...

38:13.360 --> 38:17.190
不正常数据
irregularities.

38:18.790 --> 38:20.590
安迪  下午好
Good afternoon to you, too, Andy.

38:20.660 --> 38:22.590
你的2个大客户没有
Two of your top buyers don't have valid

38:22.660 --> 38:23.960
合法社保号
Social Security numbers.

38:24.020 --> 38:26.590
我查了那个他所谓的
I checked out the Social Security numbers

38:26.660 --> 38:29.920
伽特工厂买主的社保号
of the clients he allegedly sold GATE workshops to.

38:29.990 --> 38:33.290
有些纯粹是捏造的
In some cases the numbers are just pure fabrications.

38:33.360 --> 38:36.120
但账务必须清算啊
But the checks must've cleared.

38:36.190 --> 38:39.020
他之前肯定在洗钱
He's must've been money laundering for God only knows

38:39.090 --> 38:40.560
天晓得用什么勾当
what kind of criminal exploits.

38:40.620 --> 38:42.960
关键是
The point is...

38:43.020 --> 38:46.260
如果那个执法长官拿到这份报告
if the good officer gets his hands on these papers, you know

38:46.320 --> 38:49.290
你估计就得去见国税核对员了
you're going to be up to your eyeballs in IRS auditors.

38:50.590 --> 38:53.990
我建议你跟莫拉先生说
I suggest you go tell Mr. Mara

38:54.060 --> 38:58.060
你发现布劳努的帐有问题
that you found some irregularities in Blauner's expenses.

38:58.120 --> 39:01.620
注销了私人物品  等等
Writing off personal matters, et cetera.

39:01.690 --> 39:04.690
这就能解释他为会消失
This will explain why he disappeared

39:04.760 --> 39:06.920
也可以息事宁人
and will placate the po-po.

39:07.960 --> 39:09.460
好吧
Okay.

39:17.320 --> 39:18.490
听着  侦探
Listen, Detective...

39:20.390 --> 39:22.820
把它抬起来
Pick it up! Pick it up!

39:22.890 --> 39:24.190
抬不起来  太重了
I can't, it's too heavy!

39:25.220 --> 39:26.490
支柱肯定是断了
The brace must have snapped.

39:26.560 --> 39:28.190
试试把它抬起来
Let's try and get it up!

39:29.720 --> 39:31.020
根本动不了
It's not moving!

39:32.220 --> 39:33.420
水来了
The water's coming.

39:33.490 --> 39:35.860
水来了  出来
The water's coming! Come on!

39:36.920 --> 39:39.290
我们只能把它留在那了
We got to leave it there.

39:39.360 --> 39:41.260
这样就再也拿不到"锡拉"了
But then we'll never get Scylla.

39:41.320 --> 39:44.490
我们别无选择
We don't have a choice.

39:44.560 --> 39:46.460
你没有  我有
You don't, I do.

39:46.520 --> 39:48.020
你这是干嘛
What the hell are you doing?!

39:49.190 --> 39:50.660
你这是干嘛
What the hell are you doing?!

